Package: bezdek
Type: Package
Title: Fuzzy C-Means Clustering with Optional Cluster at Infinity
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Michael Campbell", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "m.campbell@tutanota.com")
Description: Fuzzy c-means clustering (Bezdek 1981) with support for an
    optional cluster at infinity for outlier handling. The core algorithm
    is implemented in C via .Call().
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
NeedsCompilation: yes
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
